<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFCallenbachMichael_Phillips1985">Callenbach, Ernest; Michael Phillips (1985). <i><a href="http://www.well.com/user/mp/citleg.html" class="external text" title="http://www.well.com/user/mp/citleg.html" rel="nofollow">A Citizen Legislature</a></i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.well.com/user/mp/citleg.html" class="external free" title="http://www.well.com/user/mp/citleg.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.well.com/user/mp/citleg.html</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=A+Citizen+Legislature&amp;rft.aulast=Callenbach&amp;rft.aufirst=Ernest&amp;rft.au=Callenbach%2C+Ernest&amp;rft.au=Michael+Phillips&amp;rft.date=1985&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.well.com%2Fuser%2Fmp%2Fcitleg.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Demarchy"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFLe.C3.B3n1988">León, L (1988). <i><a href="http://www.socsci.kun.nl/~advdv/leonbook/leonbook.html" class="external text" title="http://www.socsci.kun.nl/~advdv/leonbook/leonbook.html" rel="nofollow">The World-Solution for World-Problems: The Problem, Its Cause, Its Solution</a></i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.socsci.kun.nl/~advdv/leonbook/leonbook.html" class="external free" title="http://www.socsci.kun.nl/~advdv/leonbook/leonbook.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.socsci.kun.nl/~advdv/leonbook/leonbook.html</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+World-Solution+for+World-Problems%3A+The+Problem%2C+Its+Cause%2C+Its+Solution&amp;rft.aulast=Le%C3%B3n&amp;rft.aufirst=L&amp;rft.au=Le%C3%B3n%2C+L&amp;rft.date=1988&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.socsci.kun.nl%2F%7Eadvdv%2Fleonbook%2Fleonbook.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Demarchy"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> (Hard copy available at the Library of Congress, Washington DC, LC Classification: H61 .L445 1988)</li>
